                <mxCell id="eO_2Dl6NA7Tksj87OyTa-694" value="经过FHLSLMaterialTranslator的编译之后，将获得完整的材质Shader代码，&#10;便会送入FMaterialShaderMap::Compile接口进行编译，存储编译后的shader代码和&#10;UniformExpression， 然后保存到FMaterialShaderMap之中。填充到MaterialTemplate.ush的宏和空缺代码段" style="text;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;rotatable=0;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;fontSize=9;strokeWidth=1;strokeColor=#82b366;fillColor=#d5e8d4;" parent="eO_2Dl6NA7Tksj87OyTa-693" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry y="26" width="360" height="44" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="eO_2Dl6NA7Tksj87OyTa-695" value="Translate()：执行HLSL转译，将表达式转译成代码块保存到对应的属性槽中。&#10;GetMaterialShaderCode()：将材质的宏、属性、表达式等数据填充到MaterialTemplate.ush并返回结果。&#10;&#10;FMaterial* Material;&#10;//关键数据，引用编译后的结果，最后会赋值给对应FMaterial存储&#10;FMaterialCompilationOutput&amp; MaterialCompilationOutput;&#10;FString MaterialTemplate：待填充或填充后的MaterialTemplate.ush字符串。" style="text;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;rotatable=0;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;fontSize=9;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" parent="eO_2Dl6NA7Tksj87OyTa-693" vertex="1">
